03/12/Post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2026-03-12" /><published>2026-03-12T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-12T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/12/Post</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/12/Post.html"><![CDATA[<p>Beauty and harmony are as necessary to you as the very breath of life.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Beauty and harmony are as necessary to you as the very breath of life.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">2026-03-11</title><link href="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/11/Post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2026-03-11" /><published>2026-03-11T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-11T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/11/Post</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/11/Post.html"><![CDATA[<p>You will gain money by a speculation or lottery.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[You will gain money by a speculation or lottery.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">2026-03-10</title><link href="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/10/Post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2026-03-10" /><published>2026-03-10T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-10T00:00:00+00:00</updated><id>https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/10/Post</id><content type="html" xml:base="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/10/Post.html"><![CDATA[<p>Never look up when dragons fly overhead.</p>]]></content><author><name></name></author><summary type="html"><![CDATA[Never look up when dragons fly overhead.]]></summary></entry><entry><title type="html">2026-03-09</title><link href="https://morsecodepodcast.github.io/2026/03/09/Post.html" rel="alternate" type="text/html" title="2026-03-09" /><published>2026-03-09T00:00:00+00:00</published><updated>2026-03-